Package: uktrade
Type: Package
Title: Accessing Data Through HMRC's API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("van der Meulen", "Peter", email = "peter.vd.meulen@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a wrapper for HMRC's newly released API. It provides convenient functions to load Overseas Trade Statistics, Regional Trade Statistics, and trader data. It also provides a function for loading custom URLs.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
  R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
  httr,
  jsonlite,
  curl,
  attempt,
  dplyr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
